Third-Party Components
----------------------

This software uses the following third-party libraries:

- @huggingface/transformers (Apache 2.0) — local ML inference runtime
- @modelcontextprotocol/sdk (MIT) — MCP server framework
- better-sqlite3 (MIT) — SQLite bindings for Node.js
- Fastify (MIT) — HTTP server framework
- Zod (MIT) — schema validation

Machine Learning Models
-----------------------

The following models are downloaded at runtime and are distributed
under their own licenses (typically Apache 2.0):

- Xenova/all-MiniLM-L6-v2 (Apache 2.0) — sentence embeddings
- Xenova/ms-marco-MiniLM-L-6-v2 (Apache 2.0) — cross-encoder reranker
- Xenova/flan-t5-small (Apache 2.0) — query expansion

See the HuggingFace model pages for full license details.
